<%@ taglib uri="http://struts.apache.org/tags-bean" prefix="bean"%>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="contents-header">
			<bean:message key="privacy.contents.heading"/>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="contents">
		<div class="text" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 0px">
			The trust you have in our site is very important to us and we take your privacy very seriously. 
			We are committed to protect your privacy and give you a secure online experience. 
			This privacy statement explains what data we collect from the site users. By accessing the Site, 
			you are consenting to this data collection described in this privacy statement.<br><br>
			
			Our primary goal in collecting your personal information is to provide you with a smooth 
			and efficient experience. It also allows us to customize our service to make 
			your experience easier. 
			Your profile is available for other members to view. 
			Members' profiles include a description and photos, likes and dislikes, individual descriptions 
			and other information helpful in determining matches. 
			Your viewable profile does not include any identifying information 
			about you such as your phone number or email address.
			 
			We do not disclose your telephone number or email address nor do we sell it 
			or make it available to any third party other than as outlined 
			in more detail in this Privacy Policy.<br><br>
			
			We collect and store certain technical and other information about 
			the online activities of our users. 
			This includes your IP address, browser type, and operating
			system. We do not use this information to identify you or to link it 
			with your matchmaking activities. 
			We do, however, track the number of people who view each page, 
			and other site usage data, in order to learn which features are the most popular 
			and thereby improve our service.<br>
			<ul type="square" style="padding-left: 10px;">
				<li>
					<b>How do you use my information?</b> <br>
					We never disclose your personal information to 
					any third party without your explicit permission. 
					We use the public information you voluntarily give us 
					to better understand who you are and provide you with customized services. <br><br>
				</li>
				<li>
					<b>How can I control or change my Information?</b> <br>
					Once you become a member of our site, your personal information 
					is stored in the My Profile section of the site.
					This section is only accessible to you using your email address and password chosen by you.  
					You may access or change your information at any time. <br><br>
				</li>
				<li>
					<b>What are cookies and how do you use them?</b> <br>
					A cookie is a small amount of data that is sent to your browser 
					from a Web server and stored on your computer's hard drive, 
					then sent back to the server by your browser each time you access 
					certain sections of the site. 
					Most cookies are "session cookies", meaning that they are automatically 
					deleted from your hard drive when you logout from our site. <br>

					You have the ability to accept or decline cookies. 
					Most Web browsers automatically accept cookies,	but you can usually 
					modify your browser setting to decline cookies if you prefer. 
					If you choose to decline cookies, you may not be able 
					to fully experience the interactive features of the our Web site. 
					<br><br>
				</li>
				<li>
					<b>Links to Other Web Sites</b> <br>
					This site may contain links to other Web sites. 
					Please be aware that this Privacy Statement applies solely to the information 
					collected on this site. 
					We are not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of other Web sites. 
					We encourage you to be aware when you are leaving this Site 
					and read the privacy statements of each and every Web site 
					that you visit before providing any personally identifiable information.
					<br><br>
				</li>
				<li>
					<b>Changes to This Privacy Statement</b> <br>
					We may occasionally update this privacy statement. 
					When we do, we will also revise the "last updated" date of the privacy statement. 
					For material changes to this privacy statement, we will notify you 
					either by placing a prominent notice on the home page of our web site 
					or by directly sending you a notification. 
					We encourage you to periodically review this privacy statement 
					to stay informed about how we are protecting the personal information we collect. 
					Your continued use of the service constitutes your agreement to this privacy statement 
					and any updates.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
